<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>wangboo</title>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/bootstrap.css' />
    <style type="text/css">
        .footer {
            padding: 19px 20px 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
        }
        .image-border{
            border: 1px solid;
            border-color: #66afe9;
            border-radius: 4px;
            width: 162px;
            height: 162px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        #content {
            background-color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
    <script src="/js/jquery-1.10.2.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="/js/changebg.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body onload="changebg()">
    <div class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
                    <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>
                <a href="#" class="navbar-brand">Wangboo</a>
            </div>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                    <li class="active"><a href="/">主页</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/">官方区</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/">灌水区</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/">职业区</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/">反馈区</a></li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                    <li><a href="/">资料</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container" id="content" style="padding-top: 60px">
        <button data-toggle="modal" data-target="#changebgModal">add</button>
        <div class="content">
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
                <% crumb.forEach(function(item) {%>
                <li><a href="<%=item.url%>"><%=item.name%></a></li>
                <%})%>
                <li class="active"><%=crumb.last().name%></li>
            </ol>
            <%-body%>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
                <p><span class="label label-default">wangboo 2014</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;版权所有 此内容系根据您的指令自动搜索的结果，不代表赞成的内容或立场</p>
        </div>

        <div class="modal fade" id="changebgModal">
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
                        <strong>选择喜欢的背景</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <div class="row" style="padding: 10px 0px 20px 10px">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class='image-border'>
                                    <a href="#"><img src='/img/robots.png' style="width: 160px;height: 160px"/></a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class='image-border'>
                                    <a href="#"><img src='/img/cartographer.png' style="width: 160px;height: 160px"/></a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class='image-border'>
                                    <a href="#"><img src='/img/escheresque_ste.png' style="width: 160px;height: 160px"/></a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class='image-border'>
                                    <a href="#"><img src='/img/cuppycake.png' style="width: 160px;height: 160px"/></a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class='image-border'>
                                    <a href="#"><img src='/img/monsturs.png' style="width: 160px;height: 160px"/></a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class='image-border'>
                                    <a href="#"><img src='/img/colours.png' style="width: 160px;height: 160px"/></a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>